<%- include('partials/header', { title }) %>

<main class="container">
    <h1 class="outbg_text">Community fridge programs</h1>
    <p class="outbg_text">
        Community fridges are shared spaces where anyone can donate or take food freely to help reduce waste and support neighbors.
    </p>

    <section class="grid">
        <article class="card">
            <h4>Public community fridges</h4>
            <p>Open-access fridges located in neighborhoods for sharing surplus food.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
            <h4>Restaurant and café partnerships</h4>
            <p>Local businesses donate unsold food to keep community fridges stocked.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
            <h4>Grocery surplus sharing</h4>
            <p>Stores contribute near-expiry or excess items that are still safe to eat.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
            <h4>Volunteer maintenance groups</h4>
            <p>Community members help clean, organize, and restock fridges regularly.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
            <h4>Food rescue coordination</h4>
            <p>Programs that collect surplus food from events, bakeries, and markets.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
            <h4>Community awareness programs</h4>
            <p>Education on reducing food waste and supporting local food sharing networks.</p>
        </article>
    </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>